uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1222%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1222%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Cyclist riding the new Nukeproof Giga full suspension mountain bike through woodland\" title=\"Nukeproof unveils the Giga\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-16-ce540de.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The low slung weight helps to make the Giga feel steadfast through the turns.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Andy Lloyd / Immediate Media</i></span></p></div><p>The first thing that came to my attention was just how well this monster of a bike pedals. When seated and climbing, the steep seat-tube angle and almost bob-free rear suspension makes climbing really quite easy going, with the only thing that feels like it’s really stifling uphill speed being the relatively slow rolling Michelin tyres.</p><p>Otherwise, considering the travel on tap, the Giga climbs far better than expected, immediately raising questions as to why you’d opt for the Mega over the Giga if you plan on riding or racing enduro.</p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=898%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1198%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=298%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=598%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=898%