e-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1213%2C809 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=403%2C269, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=808%2C539 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1213%2C809 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=553%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1107%2C738 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=553%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1107%2C738 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1222%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=406%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=814%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1222%2C815 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Cyclist riding the new Nukeproof Giga full suspension mountain bike through woodland\" title=\"Nukeproof unveils the Giga\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Nukeproof-unveils-the-Giga-15-7b569a9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=619%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Time aboard the Giga has been limited so far, but there’s no getting away from the fact that it’s more of an all-rounder than the amount of travel and its DH bike-like geometry might suggest.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Andy Lloyd / Immediate Media</i></span></p></div><p>The geometry feels well-balanced, as does the suspension, and the low-slung weight of the bike really helps to make the Giga feel planted through the turns, where it has, so far, excelled.</p><p>It’s hard to properly comment on suspension performance, having not really ridden many rough trails in my limited time aboard the bike, but the plan is to do some back-to-back testing with the Mega over the coming months before compiling a more thorough review.</p></section></div>","author":"Robin Weaver","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"adec54476b8838fe62f33023bd0cb593ed1d864d0a84bc0a719a047f24ec0548","category":"Cycling"}